<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Đăng xuất - CosmoVision</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/profile.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        .logout-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(5,8,20,0.6), rgba(5,8,20,0.6));
            color: #fff;
        }
        .logout-card {
            background: #0f1a26;
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            width: 420px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logout-card h2 { margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .logout-actions { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; margin-top:18px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logout-page">
        <div class="logout-card">
            <h2>Bạn có chắc muốn đăng xuất?</h2>
            <p>Nếu bạn đăng xuất, bạn sẽ cần đăng nhập lại để truy cập các tính năng cá nhân.</p>
            <form action="/v1/auth/logout" method="POST" class="logout-actions">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Có</button>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Không</a>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
